snippet.textDisplay:
This is an act of worship which has been highly encouraged and will bring you great reward on the Day of Judgment.

Narrated Abu Huraira:

Allah's Messenger Prophet Muhammad (PEACE BE UPON HIM) said, "Allah SWT has 99 Names, one-hundred less one; and he who memorized them all by heart will enter Paradise." (Sahih al-Bukhari 7392)
